'''Qotho''' is a recurring character in the [[Season 1|first season]]. He is played by guest star [[Dar Salim]] and debuts in the [[Winter is Coming (episode)|series premiere]]. Qotho is a [[bloodrider]] to Khal [[Drogo]]. He is killed by [[Jorah Mormont]] after Drogo falls ill. Qotho tries to prevent [[Mirri Maz Duur]] from treating Drogo and Jorah intervenes.

